{% extends '@templates/template-full-width.twig' %}

{% block page_content %}
  <div class="article">
    <div class="article__header">
      <h1 class="article__heading">{{ content['heading'] }}</h2>
      <p class="article__subheading">{{ content['subheading'] }}</p>
      <div class="article__meta"></div>
      <div class="article__shares"></div>
      <div class="article__hero">
        {% include '@atoms/images/image/responsive-image.twig' with {
          image_srcset: images.hero['image_srcset'],
          image_sizes: images.hero['image_sizes'],
          image_src: images.hero['image_src'],
          image_alt: images.hero['image_alt'],
          image_title: images.hero['image_title'],
          image_caption: images.hero['image_caption'],
          image_attribution: images.hero['image_attribution'],
        } %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="article__body">
      <div class="article__content">
        <p>A new era of patient care has begun at Butaro Hospital.</p>

        <p>After nearly two years of construction and renovation, Butaro Hospital has completed its expansion project, positioning it to offer improved care and services to the over 33,000 patients who seek treatment there each year.</p>

        <p>Dr. Joel M. Mubiligi, Executive Director of Partners In Health in Rwanda and Interim Vice Chancellor of the University of Global Health Equity, shared:</p>

        <h2>This is an Article Section Heading (H2)</h2>

        {% include '@organisms/collections/tiles/tiles.twig' with {
          images: images.embeds.single,
        } %}

        <p>The ambitious, multi-year expansion project, which Partners In Health began in December 2021 in partnership with the government, has increased the hospital’s capacity from 150 to 237 beds, doubled the number of surgeries able to be performed, and added a four-story wing, including a radiology suite, an emergency unit, and two admission oncology wards.</p>

